00:28:26.330 --> 00:28:27.390
Jika begitu,

00:28:27.790 --> 00:28:28.270
Encik Tang,

00:28:28.270 --> 00:28:30.060
apa kata pergi terus ke Menara Shisan

00:28:30.060 --> 00:28:30.960
untuk membeli kebenaran tentang Tuan Muda Jiang

00:28:30.960 --> 00:28:32.200
dan Encik Feng?

