Jadi sebab itu awak

00:28:58.510 --> 00:29:00.240
menendang Encik Feng ke dalam air.

00:29:00.350 --> 00:29:01.590
Tetapi kenapa Encik Feng

00:29:01.830 --> 00:29:03.480
menerima pesanan daripada Liu Yan?

00:29:04.890 --> 00:29:05.440
