00:29:44.530 --> 00:29:45.610
Pada pendapat anda,

00:29:45.900 --> 00:29:48.110
antara Jiang Cheng dan Feng Chuanxiang,

00:29:48.110 --> 00:29:49.940
yang manakah bercakap benar?

